Academy Award Winner Mira Sorvino (Mighty Aphrodite) plays Katherine Ballard and Bill Camp (Lincoln, 12 Years a Slave) plays "Batman" - Ballard's right-hand man. The film is produced by Eduardo Verástegui and directed by Alejandro Monteverde.
